Earlier today, I had a conversation with truck drivers about being stuck in traffic. These container vans take 6 to 12 hours just to complete a 13-kilometer drive to the toll gate going out of Metro Manila. That's 6 to 12 hours of getting stuck in a line. This is just one of many major roads that's gridlocked during the holiday season. They say Metro Manila has the worst traffic in the world; now I really feel it as you can't even travel from one city to another in a day. #everydayphilippines #everydayeverywhere #philippines #traffic #congestion #manila #trucklife #tgif #lifeintransit #traffuck 
P.S 
Godspeed to everyone who's traveling this evening in Metro Manila.
